  "lyrics": "I can take the water with it and slide it in the pool for you I can take the pride away and be there for you, yeah that's so chill It's the nights we love, it's the nights that we're never ever right It's the moments, just where it begins, never really ends Life has me on a blind, life has me on a blind, life has me on a beam And I'm blind, blind, blind, tell me I'm blind, blind, tell me I'm blind, blind, blind Yeah, I've been and I'm not at that rate at all I felt like I was the night between you It seems that I was day and I was day A little wind, a little light, a little end Can't be me, can't be friends now, it's too deep And I've been me, and I've been Everything, it never ends, for all of you Your baby ain't gone, but I better stay with the cheddar Only one thing to bring us together again, will never end This love won't be getting away I know what the music's called I love you so, where'd the music go I love you so",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 38.86000061035156,
      "text": "I can take the water with it and slide it in the pool for you",
      "start": 30.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 44.81999969482422,
      "text": "I can take the pride away and be there for you, yeah that's so chill",
      "start": 38.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 52.2400016784668,
      "text": "It's the nights we love, it's the nights that we're never ever right",
      "start": 46.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 60.279998779296875,
      "text": "It's the moments, just where it begins, never really ends",
      "start": 52.2400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 67.08000183105469,
      "text": "Life has me on a blind, life has me on a blind, life has me on a beam",
      "start": 60.959999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 73.23999786376953,
      "text": "And I'm blind, blind, blind, tell me I'm blind, blind, tell me I'm blind, blind, blind",
      "start": 67.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 78.55999755859375,
      "text": "Yeah, I've been and I'm not at that rate at all",
      "start": 73.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 83.86000061035156,
      "text": "I felt like I was the night between you",
      "start": 79.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 89.9800033569336,
      "text": "It seems that I was day and I was day",
      "start": 83.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 96.72000122070312,
      "text": "A little wind, a little light, a little end",
      "start": 89.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 101.83999633789062,
      "text": "Can't be me, can't be friends now, it's too deep",
      "start": 96.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 106.08000183105469,
      "text": "And I've been me, and I've been",
      "start": 101.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 117.76000213623047,
      "text": "Everything, it never ends, for all of you",
      "start": 108.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 124.13999938964844,
      "text": "Your baby ain't gone, but I better stay with the cheddar",
      "start": 118.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 130.67999267578125,
      "text": "Only one thing to bring us together again, will never end",
      "start": 124.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 135.36000061035156,
      "text": "This love won't be getting away",
      "start": 130.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 142.8000030517578,
      "text": "I know what the music's called",
      "start": 138.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 148.3800048828125,
      "text": "I love you so, where'd the music go",
      "start": 143.47999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 151.55999755859375,
      "text": "I love you so",
      "start": 148.74000549316406
    }
  ],
